Package TuitionManager

Class Instate

java.lang.Object
TuitionManager.Student
TuitionManager.Instate
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable
public class Instate
extends Student
Class for an Instate student, extends the Student class. Represents a student that lives in the same state as the school. Instate students have funds that they receive from the state/school.
